							"left": 832,
							"top": 512,
							"width": 304,
							"height": 169,
							"text": "Mediator Pattern (GoF)\nEMERGENCY_DETECTED ->\n  assessEmergency + dispatchTeam + prepareRoom + notifyFamily\nSEVERITY_UPDATE ->\n  updatePriority + updatePatientStatus + allocateEquipment + updateDisplay\nEMERGENCY_RESOLVED ->\n  releaseResources + notifyFamily + updateDisplay\nComponents never call each other directly."
						},
